        1. Find all the 6 stone hearts
        2. Put them (one by one or all together - it doesn't matter) 
           into the URN (after the maze of shifting walls; use the switches)
        3. Release Uukrul's Heart Of Glass 
        4. Buy obsidian hammer
        5. Arm one of your men with the hammer
        6. Come into Uukrul's trone hall
        7. Cast Heart Of Glass on the ground, so Uukrul won't be able to
           disappear
        8. The only hit that can kill Uukrul is the hit by hammer
        9. After the death of Lord Uukrul pick up the key he drops 
           and open the grate.  URXASZEL is near now. 



